Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.39,0:03:14.14,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}光をあつめて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.00,0:03:26.88,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}さよならの想い出を
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.65,0:03:33.79,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}瞳にたたえて　見つめる夢　遠く
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.79,0:03:39.04,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}壊れてしまう　うたかたのメモリー
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.40,0:03:44.59,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}寂しさの涙　そっと拭こう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.80,0:03:51.67,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}伸ばした手は観覧車　優しくとらえて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.87,0:03:56.92,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}目覚めそうな　記憶の欠片
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.89,0:04:02.85,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}うつむいて　消えてほしいと祈るけど
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.90,0:04:09.03,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}君が見つけてくれたこの声を
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.26,0:04:16.11,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}動き出した時計の針　世界はやがて色づいて
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.28,0:04:22.37,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}プラスティックな心が輝き出すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.37,0:04:27.16,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}忘れないで　おぼえていて
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.50,0:04:34.18,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}いつかまた巡り合える日まで
Comment: 0,0:03:10.00,0:03:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.39,0:03:14.14,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}光芒聚集
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.00,0:03:26.88,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}离别的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.65,0:03:33.79,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}溢满了眼眶 凝视不放的梦甚远
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.79,0:03:39.04,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}早已支离破碎 如泡沫般的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.40,0:03:44.59,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}拭去寂寞的泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.80,0:03:51.67,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}你的手如同摩天轮 温柔地带走我的心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.87,0:03:56.92,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}似乎就要回想起 残缺的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.89,0:04:02.85,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}可我却低头祈望记忆消逝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.90,0:04:09.03,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}你替我找到的 这声音
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.26,0:04:16.11,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}时针开始旋转 世界渐渐染上色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.28,0:04:22.37,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}塑胶的心亦绽放光彩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.37,0:04:27.16,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}不要忘记 请你记得
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.50,0:04:34.18,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}直至再相会的那一天
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.96,0:22:24.47,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}はぐれた君を探してたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.67,0:22:28.19,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}呼びかけた声かき消されて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.34,0:22:36.14,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}僕が握りしめたその手は　震えていたね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.25,0:22:39.97,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}ふたりの想いが
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.97,0:22:45.01,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}戻せない時間抱きしめ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.12,0:22:49.69,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}高く飛んでくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.26,0:22:54.28,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}万華鏡空にきらめいて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.28,0:22:58.11,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}君がぎこちなく微笑んでて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.20,0:23:04.09,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}愛しさ溢れてゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.22,0:23:08.83,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}光が溶けてくその前に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.84,0:23:11.94,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}心から願うんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.03,0:23:24.30,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}この瞬間を　永遠に忘れないようにと
Comment: 0,0:03:49.30,0:03:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.96,0:22:24.47,EDCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}在路上寻找你走散的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.67,0:22:28.19,EDCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}我呼唤的声响被风儿掠去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.34,0:22:36.14,EDCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}手中紧握的小手 不安的悸动着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.25,0:22:39.97,EDCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}你我彼此的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.97,0:22:45.01,EDCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}紧抱着流逝的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.12,0:22:49.69,EDCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}高高升起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.26,0:22:54.28,EDCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}万花筒夜空中亦绽放虹彩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.28,0:22:58.11,EDCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}你努力挤出僵硬的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.20,0:23:04.09,EDCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}爱意满溢而出
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.22,0:23:08.83,EDCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}在光晕染之前
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.84,0:23:11.94,EDCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}我自内心许愿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.03,0:23:24.30,EDCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}希望能永远记住这一分一秒
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.13,0:00:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}SAI终端服务一般被称为回收方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.58,0:00:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在世界各地共有29个部门
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.58,0:00:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我所就职的第一终端服务负责管辖总部所在的远东地区
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.95,0:00:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这之后又要去总部开会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.04,0:00:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}胃又疼起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.24,0:00:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小艾拉可以帮我泡杯茶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.97,0:00:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}课长别老是把艾拉当作泡茶的使唤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在她可是司的执行者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.18,0:00:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请在这里签字
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.84,0:00:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我只不过是还没改掉习惯而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.97,0:00:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哟 诸位好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.61,0:00:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.45,0:00:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}縹康孝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.79,0:00:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们的观测者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.28,0:00:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}别看那样他可是在这里工作了快十年的老手了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.49,0:01:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你这小子 放着工作不做去哪里偷懒了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.04,0:01:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}当然是带薪休假或者出差什么的了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.28,0:01:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}原来去女人那里叫做出差啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.78,0:01:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我还是第一次这样听说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.80,0:01:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}记住这个绝不会吃亏的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.60,0:01:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你这
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.19,0:01:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.49,0:01:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}康孝君那是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.91,0:01:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真棒 艾拉你泡的茶依然是最棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.01,0:01:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.95,0:01:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你就是那个人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.46,0:01:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和艾拉组队的新人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.48,0:01:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我叫水柿司
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.25,0:01:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.48,0:01:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你就是那个啥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.92,0:01:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和伍堂部长打招呼 照顾进来的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.63,0:01:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我说呀 你和部长是什么样的关系呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.40,0:01:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请一定要告诉我呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.13,0:02:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为患了阑尾炎结果应试失败啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.13,0:02:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是的…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.81,0:02:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没有必要就不要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.32,0:02:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘛随便了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.49,0:02:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}感谢你的父亲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.86,0:02:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这次是特例
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.67,0:02:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是如果我认为你并不适合在我们公司工作的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.87,0:02:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我会立刻开除你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.48,0:02:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}记住了吗
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.17,0:02:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}部长和我父亲认识
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.12,0:02:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.16,0:02:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}康孝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.25,0:02:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我和你有点话要说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.91,0:02:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雪莉~我的搭档呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.03,0:02:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂喂 再多来点笑容吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.87,0:02:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们这里的女孩子 为什么都表情这么可怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.51,0:02:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都是因为你这几天丢下工作不管的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.13,0:02:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}关于这个 还希望你可以充分的说明一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.27,0:02:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}唉呀 但是我肚子有点饿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.68,0:02:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想先去吃点东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.67,0:03:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这个笑话可真是好笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.93,0:03:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不要太紧张 放松点好好干哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.13,0:03:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}救命…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.38,0:04:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\fad(417,417)\pos(768,613)\39\blur5\bord3\3c&H7A46F0&}#02   不想扯后腿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.38,0:04:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\fad(417,417)\39\bord0.5\3c&H4C49B7&\pos(768,613)}#02   不想扯后腿
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.18,0:04:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你就是柳丰吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.73,0:04:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们并不是可疑的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.13,0:05:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}老实地将那边的马克思交给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.86,0:05:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们是终端服务 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.80,0:05:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}你们搞什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.52,0:05:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}马克思快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.87,0:05:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂等等 为什么要吓唬他们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.51,0:05:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}错误 我没有听清楚 请再说一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.36,0:05:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}总之先追上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.51,0:05:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.75,0:05:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂 没事吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.97,0:05:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}呆着别动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.63,0:05:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}被他们跑掉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.93,0:05:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看来又要写检讨了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.04,0:06:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.45,0:06:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.69,0:06:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们先回去了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.55,0:06:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这都第几次了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.04,0:06:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第三次…了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.77,0:06:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我已经给你安排相当轻松的工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.25,0:06:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}结果三次都被拒签同意书
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.04,0:06:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.23,0:06:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果有好好和艾拉建立了信赖关系的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.81,0:06:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}应该不会变成这样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.66,0:06:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.66,0:06:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}毕竟是走后门的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.67,0:06:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不费一丝辛劳就进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.37,0:06:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}完全派不上用场
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.01,0:06:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司他…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.84,0:06:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抱歉 下次我会注意的
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.37,0:06:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可恶 司那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.47,0:06:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可能确实说的太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.13,0:06:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}满总是直言不讳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.71,0:07:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说完又开始后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.16,0:07:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喔 你和司吵架了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}才没有那么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.59,0:07:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘴上说着讨厌讨厌其实很喜欢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.96,0:07:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}清清纯纯的很棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.62,0:07:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啥 我和司才不是这种关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.12,0:07:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不要害羞嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.77,0:07:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我都说了不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.66,0:07:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}满
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.21,0:07:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.67,0:07:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉情况怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.80,0:07:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.88,0:07:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我觉得和平时没什么两样…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.78,0:07:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是吗
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.61,0:07:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.87,0:07:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天下班后有空吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.26,0:07:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.07,0:07:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有空的吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.40,0:07:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.45,0:08:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂 你有在喝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.32,0:08:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我一开始就说我还未成年了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.61,0:08:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是没用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.64,0:08:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}话说 你和艾拉有好好相处吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.31,0:08:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.91,0:08:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}「不知道她在想什么」之类的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.29,0:08:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}能告诉我关于艾拉的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.82,0:08:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}香月以前和艾拉是搭档吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.75,0:08:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我告诉你也没有什么意义
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.85,0:08:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果本人不去互相理解也是白搭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.28,0:08:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}话是这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.33,0:08:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也觉得很过意不去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.88,0:08:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}把她交给你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.27,0:08:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你们这么多的失误
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.42,0:08:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大概也是因为艾拉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.26,0:08:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.34,0:08:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.66,0:08:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虽然艾拉是个那样的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.89,0:08:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你可要好好和她相处哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.59,0:09:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拜托你这种事我也是醉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.37,0:09:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 我想和艾拉进一步搞好关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.36,0:09:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.16,0:09:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你这家伙是萝莉控吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.27,0:09:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.60,0:09:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}老板再来一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.30,0:09:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再说了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.87,0:09:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}课长和总部总说要提高什么工作效率
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.52,0:09:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}根本就是胡来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.40,0:09:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.90,0:09:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也做了将近十年了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.46,0:09:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}到现在也看不到正确答案
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.47,0:09:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谁知道到底该如何销毁回忆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.53,0:09:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谁都不会知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.01,0:09:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如何销毁回忆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.28,0:10:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你有在听吗 新人！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.59,0:10:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}香 香月小姐 好痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.77,0:10:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}耶 香月喝多啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.69,0:10:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}康孝先生怎么也在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.54,0:10:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也是这里的常客
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.57,0:10:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这家伙喝了多少杯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.42,0:10:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只有三杯左右吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.32,0:10:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}难道说她酒量很差？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.10,0:10:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}很差
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.93,0:10:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.46,0:10:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}总之我先送她回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.61,0:10:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}已经是常事了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.51,0:10:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 你回来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.22,0:10:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.32,0:10:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 关门就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.18,0:10:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这样啊 那就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.85,0:10:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.09,0:10:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}您辛苦了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.00,0:10:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\c&H000000&\fs30\bord0\1a&H80&\frz7.458\pos(674,261)\frx344\fry10}艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.00,0:10:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\c&H000000&\fs28\bord0\1a&H80&\frz7.458\pos(584,457)\frx348\fry10}\h\h\h\h\h\h\h单元测验房\N[训练]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.53,0:10:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}单元测验房？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.77,0:11:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是哪里
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.10,0:11:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 总部大楼里竟然还有这种设施啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.10,0:11:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.17,0:11:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是艾拉的观测者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.73,0:11:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.64,0:11:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.03,0:11:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们是终端服务部的专属工程师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.76,0:11:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我是绘瑠 这位是铁黑右次郎师父
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.24,0:11:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请跪拜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.81,0:11:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.63,0:11:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}无视我吗 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.06,0:11:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在采集数据
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.83,0:11:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}数据？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.59,0:11:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这是在测量身体能力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.95,0:11:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}讨厌 居然偷看少女的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.20,0:11:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是个糟糕的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.44,0:11:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}她经常会来做这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.15,0:11:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是 只是和小司搭档之后才经常来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.24,0:12:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小司？
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.92,0:12:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为最近负担也变大了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.87,0:12:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}保养的次数也增多了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.77,0:12:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我倒希望她能休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.07,0:12:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}负担？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.62,0:12:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}身体的负担
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.47,0:12:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为以前就只是倒倒茶而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.15,0:12:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而现在回到现场工作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.75,0:12:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}情况当然是不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}绘瑠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.58,0:12:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}别光动嘴不动手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.69,0:12:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是 对不起 师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.56,0:12:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不过看起来…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.47,0:12:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有点惨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.03,0:12:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.81,0:12:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}擅自跑过来看 抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.97,0:12:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没什么 我也没有躲藏着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.64,0:13:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要喝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.32,0:13:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.34,0:13:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为什么突然要训练
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.60,0:13:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}难道是在介意工作上的失误吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.49,0:13:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}时隔很久回到现场工作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.76,0:13:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}身体没能像想像中那样行动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.80,0:13:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在的我在拖司的后退
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.48,0:13:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一定是因为空档期的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.55,0:13:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}很快就会找回感觉的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.14,0:13:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是 不只是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.65,0:13:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和持有者沟通的时候也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.39,0:13:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好像立刻就会变得很僵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.14,0:13:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.05,0:13:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}暖…因为没有做暖机运转
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.10,0:13:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？ 暖机运转…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.04,0:13:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}又不是以前的汽车
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.17,0:13:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的需要吗
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.86,0:13:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一定要解决
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.81,0:13:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.53,0:14:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}作为你的执行者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.65,0:14:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不能再给你添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.55,0:14:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果司已经觉得受不了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.72,0:14:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那就只能解散我们的搭档关系了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.41,0:14:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢谢你的茶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.30,0:14:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我这人呢 其实很墨守成规的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.85,0:14:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}工作的话守规矩还是很重要的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.74,0:14:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以来这以后 我还是尽量试着读懂规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.54,0:14:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的是相当的应付啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.94,0:14:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}「临机应变地对应」之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.10,0:14:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}「用最好的方法应对」之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.57,0:14:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}具体的内容一点都没写
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.95,0:14:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以 我能做的就是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.33,0:14:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}按照规则上写的临机应变地对应而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.15,0:14:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}临机应变？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.84,0:14:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}比如说 和持有者之间的交涉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.19,0:15:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不让艾拉来做 而让我来做怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.86,0:15:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是观测者的工作是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.93,0:15:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}监督搭档的执行者 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.61,0:15:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虽然我知道这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.57,0:15:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但好不容易能成为搭档
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.93,0:15:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}互相帮助一下也挺好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.30,0:15:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.38,0:15:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在艾拉找回感觉之前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.54,0:15:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}依靠一下我这种人也挺好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.74,0:15:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要不要这样试一次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.98,0:15:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.24,0:15:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就这样决定的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.80,0:15:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就尽力来制定自己的规则吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.64,0:15:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我…去下厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.65,0:15:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.59,0:15:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.22,0:15:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我…会努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.80,0:16:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}很好！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.40,0:16:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对不起 我下次会注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.83,0:16:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是没意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.25,0:16:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.65,0:16:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早啊 满
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.00,0:16:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}呐 你觉得司这人怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.23,0:16:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}才…才没有什么奇怪的意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.70,0:16:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和司搭档是不是成为你的负担了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.64,0:16:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我感觉你最近很明显地在勉强自己
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.76,0:16:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不必对司这样的新人太客气的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.65,0:16:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不愿意的话就说出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.91,0:17:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你只是被课长强行和他组队的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.71,0:17:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}满
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.00,0:17:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不用担心我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.09,0:17:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且…拖后腿的人是我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.03,0:17:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.83,0:17:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.14,0:17:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那家伙真是 果然是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.23,0:17:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}呜嘎！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.61,0:17:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}竟然不向我如实汇报
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.49,0:17:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.44,0:17:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}「不找借口才帅气」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.30,0:17:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你难道是这样想的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.23,0:17:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我说过那么多次不要再把自己当学生了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.33,0:17:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}满 不要太生司的气了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.67,0:17:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我知道了 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.92,0:17:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啊 首先是倾听对方的话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.35,0:17:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只是附和对方就能让人放心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.30,0:17:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早啊 在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.90,0:17:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.02,0:17:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司在问我一些奇怪的问题呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.95,0:18:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和回收对象的所有者交涉时都需要注意些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.22,0:18:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.28,0:18:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这么说 难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.29,0:18:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你到底是无能还是蠢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.56,0:18:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这又怎么了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.62,0:18:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吉芙提尔是有感情的 持有者也是有感情的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.95,0:18:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.85,0:18:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这是从香月那里现学现卖来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.92,0:18:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 就是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.61,0:18:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}听着 仅仅回收吉芙提尔是不够的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.31,0:18:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}否则的话 我们的工作只能带来悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.04,0:18:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}重要的是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.12,0:18:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要依顺吉芙提尔和持有者双方的意愿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.20,0:18:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}双方都要…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.68,0:18:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大概只有我们这里会这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.45,0:18:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就连本部也对这种方法避而不用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.40,0:18:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是 因为我是赞成香月的想法的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.64,0:18:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以既然你来这里工作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.43,0:18:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就要实践这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.37,0:18:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我明白了 谢谢你教给我这些
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.87,0:18:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哼 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.00,0:19:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂 塞克 要去工作了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.19,0:19:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 现在就去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.83,0:19:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天真的有那么要紧的工作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.68,0:19:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我觉得没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.95,0:19:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好了快点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.27,0:19:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}知道了 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.18,0:19:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.19,0:19:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还有 司
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.23,0:19:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}上次对你说了很多过分的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.03,0:19:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.81,0:19:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.91,0:19:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}满一大早就这么激动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.40,0:19:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一定是到了复杂的年纪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.44,0:19:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我懂的 我家的女儿也是完全不听我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.05,0:19:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请别说那种令人悲伤的话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.98,0:19:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 差不多就这样了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.19,0:19:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哟 真是努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.68,0:19:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 你怎么来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.32,0:19:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雪莉太会使唤人了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.57,0:20:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.90,0:20:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我在做自己用的工作手册
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.28,0:20:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那可真是了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.72,0:20:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没什么 比起我 艾拉更努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.19,0:20:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}单元测试房啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.21,0:20:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为了找回在空白期里丢失的感觉 每天都在进行训练呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.48,0:20:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘛 不管能不能找回感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.33,0:20:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}冒冒失失的样子大概是不会变了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.16,0:20:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个孩子真是厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.06,0:20:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明知是徒劳却还是这么努力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.36,0:20:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}徒劳？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.59,0:20:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉就是那个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.13,0:20:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}到底是什么意思呢 徒劳什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.15,0:20:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个…艾拉的身体测试数据
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.90,0:20:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你看过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.00,0:20:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}稍微瞥到过一点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.43,0:20:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是不是一直在下降？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.67,0:20:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对 不是因此才为了弥补空白期而进行训练的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.86,0:20:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吉芙提尔和人类还有其他机器人一样要学习
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.89,0:21:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是 吉芙提尔并没有空白期的概念
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.58,0:21:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他们体内原本就没有植入遗忘功能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.00,0:21:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以这到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.97,0:21:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不管怎样训练都是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.76,0:21:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉以后一直会是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.44,0:21:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那孩子自己也应该明白的才对
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.68,0:21:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然是因为我太不可靠了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.83,0:21:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}才让她那么勉强自己的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.93,0:21:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.21,0:22:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢谢 我…会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.74,0:22:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都被她那样说了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.88,0:22:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}柳丰先生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.84,0:22:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}又是你们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.25,0:22:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请听我说完
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.97,0:22:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们是SAI公司的终端服务人员
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.46,0:22:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是来通知您马克思的回收时间的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.19,0:22:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}回收？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.35,0:22:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}上次让您受惊了 非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.56,0:22:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是吗…这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.21,0:22:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要回收了啊 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.01,0:22:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}上次逃走了真是抱歉
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.28,0:23:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是司的报告书？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.42,0:23:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 他们两个意外的很合拍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.76,0:23:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这不是挺好的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.19,0:23:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不过还真是让我吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.36,0:23:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你居然什么都没跟他说
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.42,0:23:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.24,0:23:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}别装了 你没和他说的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.89,0:23:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉所剩的寿命还有2000小时的那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.18,0:24:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
